The evidence with the title 'Cuba says economy shrank this year in tandem with Venezuela crisis ' says Dec 27, 2016  ... Cuba 's economy shrank 0.9 percent this year in tandem with the crisis in key trading partner Venezuela , president Raul Castro told the National Assembly  ... That has boosted remittances and the tourism sector , helped the economy grow on average at close to 3 percent each year between 2011 and 2015 . 
